import React from 'react'
import { Center, Square, Circle , Text} from "native-base";


function DepositScreen() {
  return <>
    <Center>
        <Text>
            Minimum amount: 0.0003
            If you do not have bitcoin, you can buy it Click here
        </Text>
    </Center>
  </>
  
}

export default DepositScreen
